            <V n="text" t="single">
              <T n="single">0x14C663FB<!--Today is a <b>Full Moon</b>, so here's what I can share with you, Kiddo:\n\nYou probably want to know more about The Ancestor. Y'know, the giant face carved into the side of that cliff in Whispering Glen. The Scrappity Restroom...or Scribbly Toilet...or whatever you kids call complete monstrosities these days. I'm so old my limbs creak and groan, and even <i>I</i> have no idea who that's supposed to be. It's been here as long as anyone can remember! The local Sims all gather to dance or something at the <b>Moon Revelry</b>. Hooligans. All I can really say is, I would rather whoever carved it had left that dang cliff alone; the landscape would have been better with a more natural beauty—like me!--></T>
