            <V n="text" t="single">
              <T n="single">0x3D6001C2<!--Looks like you've already gotten this Moon's Whisper, Kiddo! Here's what you will learn about if you come back on each Lunar Phase:\n\n• <b>New Moon</b>: Whispering Glen Crater\n• <b>Waxing Crescent</b>: The Baleful Bog\n• <b>First Quarter</b>: Alice and her Offspring\n• <b>Waxing Gibbous</b>: Moppy the Goat\n• <b>Full Moon</b>: The Ancestor\n• <b>Waning Gibbous</b>: Specters\n• <b>Third Quarter</b>: Ravenwood\n• <b>Waning Crescent</B>: Me!--></T>
